msgid "About Us"
msgstr "关于我们"

#: ../../source/about_us.md:3
msgid ""
"**IR-SIM** was created and is maintained by Ruihua Han ([Home "
"page](https://hanruihua.github.io/), Ph.D., PostDoc @ The University of "
"Hong Kong), who initialized the project in 2023."
msgstr ""
"**IR-SIM** 由韩瑞华（[个人主页](https://hanruihua.github.io/)，香港大学博士、博士后）创建并维护，他于 "
"2023 年发起本项目。"

#: ../../source/about_us.md:5
msgid "Contributors"
msgstr "贡献者"

#: ../../source/about_us.md:7
msgid ""
"Huge thanks to everyone who has contributed code, examples, bug reports, "
"and ideas on GitHub"
msgstr "衷心感谢每一位在 GitHub 上贡献代码、示例、Bug 反馈与想法的朋友。"

#: ../../source/about_us.md:23
msgid ""
"See the full, always up-to-date list on the [GitHub contributors "
