#~ msgid "The Author"
#~ msgstr "作者"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Ruihua is a robotics researcher working"
#~ " on robot navigation, motion planning, "
#~ "and learning-based control. He built "
#~ "IR-SIM as a lightweight, YAML-"
#~ "driven simulator that makes it easy "
#~ "to prototype and test navigation, "
#~ "control, and reinforcement learning algorithms"
#~ " with minimal setup and hardware —"
#~ " the tool he wished he had for"
#~ " his own research."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "韩瑞华是一名机器人方向的研究者，主要研究机器人导航、运动规划与基于学习的控制。他开发 IR-"
#~ "SIM，是希望提供一个轻量、以 YAML "
#~ "驱动的仿真器，让用户能够以最少的配置与硬件，快速搭建并测试导航、控制与强化学习算法——这正是他在自己的研究中一直想要的工具。"

